%h2 Preview

= link_to "Click here", form, target: '_blank'
to preview your signup.

%br
%br
%br
- if form.draft?
  = form_for form, url: form_update_preview_path(form) do |f|
    = f.submit "Save as Draft", class: 'blue'
    = f.submit "Publish & Send Invites", class: 'orange'

- else
  - if form.has_unsent_invites?
    = form_for form, url: form_send_invites_path(form) do |f|
      = f.submit "Send Unsent Invites (#{form.unsent_invites.count})", class: 'orange'
